sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Script as install.sh
    participant FS as File System
    participant Pip as pip
    participant Desktop as Desktop Environment

    User->>Script: ./install.sh
    Script->>FS: mkdir ~/.local/share/applications

    alt venv does not exist
        Script->>FS: python3 -m venv venv
        Script->>Pip: pip install browser_cookie3 cloudscraper
        Pip-->>Script: Dependencies installed
    end

    Script->>FS: Create .desktop file
    Script->>FS: chmod +x claude_usage_widget.py
    Script-->>User: Installation complete

    User->>Desktop: Search "Claude Usage"
    Desktop->>FS: Read .desktop file
    Desktop->>Script: Execute widget
